<title>USA: Veritas,Openvision holders OK deal.</title>
<headline>Veritas,Openvision holders OK deal.</headline>
<dateline>MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif. 1997-04-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Veritas Software Corp and OpenVision Technologies said their merger was approved by shareholders of both companies and will be effective at the close of business today.</p>
<p>As previously announced, Veritas will issue 7.5 million new shares of Veritas stock in exchange for about 21.7 million outstanding shares and options of OpenVision stock at an exchange rate of 0.346 shares of Veritas for each share of OpenVision stock.  The deal will be accounted for as a tax-free pooling of interests.</p>
